"The political differences between the elite and the people are larger than the differences among the people"},"4":{"Display":"I would rather be represented by a citizen than by a specialized politician"},"5":{"Display":"Elected officials talk too much and take too little action"},"6":{"Display":"Politics is ultimately a struggle between good and evil"},"7":{"Display":"What people call 'compromise' in politics is really just selling out on one's principles"},"8":{"Display":"Interest groups have too much influence over political decisions"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7","8"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":9,"NextAnswerId":6,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Very much disagree"},"2":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"3":{"Display":"Neutral"},"4":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"5":{"Display":"Very much agree"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID303","SecondaryAttribute":"We are interested in how people experience the profound. Below are a series of statements taken f...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"We are interested in how people experience the\nprofound. Below are a series of statements taken\nfrom relevant websites. Please read each statement and take a moment to think about what it\nmight mean. Then please rate how \u201cprofound\u201d\nyou think it is. Profound means \u201cof deep meaning; of great and broadly inclusive significance.\u201d","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Bullshit receptivity","QuestionID":"QID303","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"We are interested in how people experience the profound. Below are a series of statements taken f...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Hidden meaning transforms unparalleled abstract beauty"},"3":{"Display":"Wholeness quiets infinite phenomena"},"4":{"Display":"Good health imparts reality to subtle creativity"},"5":{"Display":"The future explains irrational facts"},"6":{"Display":"Imagination is inside exponential space time events"},"12":{"Display":"We are in the midst of a self-aware blossoming of being that will align us with the nexus itself"},"13":{"Display":"Consciousness consists of frequencies of quantum energy. \u201cQuantum\u201d means an unveiling of the unrestricted"},"14":{"Display":"Consciousness is the growth of coherence, and of us"},"16":{"Display":"We are in the midst of a high-frequency blossoming of interconnectedness that will give us access to the quantum soup itself"},"17":{"Display":"Today, science tells us that the essence of nature is joy"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","4","3","5","6","12","13","14","16","17"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":20,"NextAnswerId":6,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Not at all profound"},"2":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"3":{"Display":"Fairly profound"},"4":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"5":{"Display":"Very profound"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID304","SecondaryAttribute":"Please indicate to what extent you believe the following statements are true.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please indicate to what extent you believe the following statements are true.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Conspiracy belief","QuestionID":"QID304","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceCol