rif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Trust can be broken down into two main components: competence and motive.&nbsp;Trust with respect to <strong>competence<\/strong> concerns your confidence that the person you need to trust is knowledgeable, skillful, qualified, and capable of providing you with clear and accurate information.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">Regarding vaccine and health information, I trust the <b>competence<\/b> of:<\/span><\/font><br>\n<br>\n<span style=\"font-family:\n&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Trust_competence","QuestionID":"QID365","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Trust can be broken down into two main components: competence and motive.\u00a0Trust with respect to c...","Choices":{"4":{"Display":"US government health agencies"},"9":{"Display":"Scientists"},"14":{"Display":"Pharmaceutical companies"},"15":{"Display":"The World Health Organization"},"16":{"Display":"Mainstream media outlets"},"17":{"Display":"My healthcare provider"}},"ChoiceOrder":["4","9","14","15","16","17"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":18,"NextAnswerId":14,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"ColumnLabels":[{"Display":"Not at all","IsLabelDefault":false},{"Display":"Completely","IsLabelDefault":false}],"Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"None"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID366","SecondaryAttribute":"This next set of questions addresses the concept of trust.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14.6667px;\">This next set of questions addresses the concept of trust.<br><br><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Trust_exp","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"This next set of questions addresses the concept of trust.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID366","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID367","SecondaryAttribute":"Trust with respect to motive deals with the intent of the person with whom you need to trust. Tha...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Trust with respect to <b>motive<\/b> deals with the intent of the person with whom you need to trust. That is, do they have your best interest at heart, or are their intentions good?&nbsp;Having good intentions means these groups or people really care about your health and well-being. They would NOT sacrifice your health and well-being for things like making a profit, winning elections, securing one's position of power, or other selfish considerations.<br>\n<br>\nRegarding vaccine and health information, I trust the&nbsp;<strong>motives<\/strong><em>&nbsp;<\/em>of:<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Trust_motivation","QuestionID":"QID367","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","