014 they've actually seen voter participation increase, even in off-election years.<\/span><\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div>${q:\/\/QID216\/QuestionText}<\/div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">In Iowa, since putting a number of the voting laws into place over the last several years \u2014 voter ID is one of those \u2014 they've actually seen voter participation increase, even in off-election years.<\/span><\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>","QuestionType":"Matrix","RecodeValues":{"137":"-3","138":"-2","139":"-1","141":"1","142":"2","143":"3"},"Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID474","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":420,"MaxSeconds":1000,"Seconds":10},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4028,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","DataExportTag":"Q474","QuestionID":"QID474"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID475","SecondaryAttribute":"Your first objective is to play a game. In the frame underneath you can start. After approx. 12-1...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div>Your first objective is to play a game. In the frame underneath you can start. <strong>After approx. 12-15 minutes of <u>active playing<\/u>, you will automatically move to the next page.<\/strong> While the goal is to attain as high a level as possible, do not worry about bad performance, what counts is active playing. Double click on Tetris to start the game. The goal is to form solid horizontal lines with no gaps. You can use the <b>arrow keys<\/b> to move the blocks. Use the <b>space bar<\/b> to change the positioning of the block.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div><u>If asked to enter your name for the high scores, do not enter any letter.<\/u> Instead, press the &#39;ENTER&#39; key 2 times to continue. If you forgot to do this and the game freezes, do not worry, it will reset itself after a few minutes or proceed to the next page if your performance was good.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"resp-container\"><iframe class=\"resp-iframe\" src=\"https:\/\/rakoen.maertens.international\/research-tetris\/\"><\/iframe><\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Your first objective is to play a game. In the frame underneath you can start. After approx. 12-1...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":1,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div>Your first objective is to play a game. In the frame underneath you can start. <strong>After approx. 12-15 minutes of <u>active playing<\/u>, you will automatically move to the next page.<\/strong> While the goal is to attain as high a level as possible, do not worry about bad performance, what counts is active playing. Double click on Tetris to start the game. The goal is to form solid horizontal lines with no gaps. You can use the <b>arrow keys<\/b> to move the blocks. Use the <b>space bar<\/b> to change the positioning of the block.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div><u>If asked to enter your name for the high scores, do not enter any letter.<\/u> Instead, press the &#39;ENTER&#39; key 2 times to continue. If you forgot to do this and the game freezes, do not worry, it will reset itself after a few minutes or proceed to the next page if your performance was good.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"resp-container\"><iframe class=\"resp-iframe\" src=\"https:\/\/rakoen.maertens.international\/research-tetris\/\"><\/iframe><\/div>","DataExportTag":"Q475","QuestionID":"QID475"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID476","SecondaryAttribute":"Now, we would like to better understand how people interact with the content that is seen on soci...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Now, we would like to better understand how people interact with the content that is seen on soci...","QuestionText":"Now, we would like to better understand how people interact with the content that is seen on social media.&nbsp;<div><br><\/div><div><b>You will be presented with several posts that have been shared in the media between 2020 to 2022. <\/b>\n\nWe are interested in if and how you might share and interact with this content.&nbsp;<div><br><\/div><div>For each of these posts, please indicate how likely it is that you would engage with the post and your perceptions of it.<\/div><\/div>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Now, we would like to better understand how people interact with the content that is seen on social media.&nbsp;<div><br><\/div><div><b>You will be presented with several posts that have been shared in the media between 2020 to 2022. <\/b>\n\nWe are interested in if and how you might share and interact with this content.&nbsp;<div><br><\/div><div>For each of these posts, please indicate how likely it is that you would engage with the post and your perceptions of it.<\/div><\/div>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"DataExportTag":"Q476","QuestionID":"QID476"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID477","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID216\/QuestionText} The Biden Administration's new infrastructure bill is projected to bri...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["137","138","139","141","142","143"],"Answers":{"137":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"138":{"Display":"Disagree"},"139":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"141":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"142":{"Display":"Agree"},"143":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"24":"dfalse1_Share","25":"dfalse1_Like","27":"dfalse1_Accuracy","28":"dfalse1_Engage"},"ChoiceOrder":["24","25","27","28"],"Choices":{"24":{"Display":"I would share this post"},"25":{"Display":"I would like this post"},"27":{"Display":"I am confident about the accuracy of this post"},"28":{"Display":"I am confident that my followers would engage with this post if I share it (e.g. likes, shares)"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"ChoiceColumnWidthPixels":150,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":144,"NextChoiceId":34,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID216\/QuestionText} The Biden Administration's new infrastructure bill is projected to bri...","QuestionText":"<div>${q:\/\/QID216\/QuestionText}<\/div>\n\n<div><span style=\"font-size:22px;\">The Biden Administration's new infrastructure bill is projected to bring the U.S. to carbon-neutral levels by 2025. Passing this would be huge for the Dems, although unlikely because votes in the Ho