d things. Just look at this recent U.S. poll from Quinnipiac showing the president's approval rating plummeting to just above 30%!! <\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"RecodeValues":{"1":"-3","2":"-2","3":"-1","4":"1","5":"2","6":"3"},"DataExportTag":"ManTrueBW2","QuestionID":"QID516"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID517","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText} Georgia state law allows a losing candidate to request a recount if th...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Disagree"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"4":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"5":{"Display":"Agree"},"6":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"CtlTrueBW1_Share","2":"CtlTrueBW1_Like","3":"CtlTrueBW1_Accuracy","4":"CtlTrueBW1_Manip","5":"CtlTrueBW1_ManipConf"},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","3","1","2"],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would share this post on social media"},"2":{"Display":"I would 'like' this post on social media"},"3":{"Display":"This is an accurate post"},"4":{"Display":"This is a manipulative post"},"5":{"Display":"I am confident in my assessment of this post's manipulativeness"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":7,"NextChoiceId":8,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText} Georgia state law allows a losing candidate to request a recount if th...","QuestionText":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<strong><i> <\/i><br>\nGeorgia state law allows a losing candidate to request a recount if the margin between the candidates is within 0.5%. In 2020, Biden led by a margin of 12,670 votes or 0.23% of the roughly 5 million ballots cast.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionText_Unsafe":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<strong><i> <\/i><br \/>\nMy grandmother told me she was 15 the last time she saw minimum wage and inflation increase together, and she had to file for BANKRUPTCY almost losing the house I grew up in. Now it&#39;s happening AGAIN and people everywhere are suffering! Meanwhile, the federal minimum wage hasn&#39;t increased for 10 years. This is tragic!<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"RecodeValues":{"1":"-3","2":"-2","3":"-1","4":"1","5":"2","6":"3"},"DataExportTag":"CtlTrueBW1","QuestionID":"QID517"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID518","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}A Georgia State LAW says that a losing candidate can request a recount...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Disagree"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"4":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"5":{"Display":"Agree"},"6":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"ManTrueBW1_Share","2":"ManTrueBW1_Like","3":"ManTrueBW1_Accuracy","4":"ManTrueBW1_Manip","5":"ManTrueBW1_ManipConf"},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","3","1","2"],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would share this post on social media"},"2":{"Display":"I would 'like' this post on social media"},"3":{"Display":"This is an accurate post"},"4":{"Display":"This is a manipulative post"},"5":{"Display":"I am confident in my assessment of this post's manipulativeness"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":7,"NextChoiceId":8,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}A Georgia State LAW says that a losing candidate can request a recount...","QuestionText":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<br>\n<strong>A Georgia State LAW says that a losing candidate can request a recount IF the margin between the candidates is within 0.5%. Laws are passed by the majority vote, and they exist for a reason! In 2020, Biden led by a margin of 12,670 votes or 0.25% of the roughly 5 million ballots cast. Myself and everyone I've spoken to agrees Trump deserved a recount.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionText_Unsafe":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<br>\n<strong>It\u2019s been over 50 years since minimum wage and inflation increased together, then over a decade since the federal minimum went up at all.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"RecodeValues":{"1":"-3","2":"-2","3":"-1","4":"1","5":"2","6":"3"},"DataExportTag":"ManTrueBW1","QuestionID":"QID518"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID519","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText} Variations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot oc...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Disagree"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"4":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"5":{"Display":"Agree"},"6":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"CtlTrueCT1_Share","2":"CtlTrueCT1_Like","3":"CtlTrueCT1_Accuracy","4":"CtlTrueCT1_Manip","5":"CtlTrueCT1_ManipConf"},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","3","1","2"],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would share this post on social media"},"2":{"Display":"I would 'like' this post on social media"},"3":{"Display":"This is an accurate post"},"4":{"Display":"This is a manipulative post"},"5":{"Display":"I am confident in my assessment of this post's manipulativeness"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":7,"NextChoiceId":8,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText} Variations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot oc...","QuestionText":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<strong><i> <\/i><br>\nVariations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot occur in every election and do not by themselves indicate fraud or issues with voting technology.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionText_Unsafe":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<strong><i> <\/i><br \/>\nMy grandmother told me she was 15 the last time she saw minimum wage and inflation increase together, and she had to file for BANKRUPTCY almost losing the house I grew up in. Now it&#39;s happening AGAIN and people everywhere are suffering! Meanwhile, the federal minimum wage hasn&#39;t increased for 10 years. This is tragic!<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"RecodeValues":{"1":"-3","2":"-2","3":"-1","4":"1","5":"2","6":"3"},"DataExportTag":"CtlTrueCT1","QuestionID":"QID519"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID520","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}Variations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot occ...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Disagree"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"4":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"5":{"Display":"Agree"},"6":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"ManTrueCT1_Share","2":"ManTrueCT1_Like","3":"ManTrueCT1_Accuracy","4":"ManTrueCT1_Manip","5":"ManTrueCT1_ManipConf"},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","3","1","2"],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would share this post on social media"},"2":{"Display":"I would 'like' this post on social media"},"3":{"Display":"This is an accurate post"},"4":{"Display":"This is a manipulative post"},"5":{"Display":"I am confident in my assessment of this post's manipulativeness"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":7,"NextChoiceId":8,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}Variations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot occ...","QuestionText":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<br>\n<strong>Variations in vote totals for different contests on the same ballot occur in every election and provide EVIDENCE of ballot tampering by hidden forces. You can't tell me there isn't a way for those who made the machines to deliberately mess with the outcome. That has fraud written all over it folks.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionText_Unsafe":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText}<br>\n<strong>It\u2019s been over 50 years since minimum wage and inflation increased together, then over a decade since the federal minimum went up at all.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nFor the content above, to what extent do you agree with the following statements?","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"RecodeValues":{"1":"-3","2":"-2","3":"-1","4":"1","5":"2","6":"3"},"DataExportTag":"ManTrueCT1","QuestionID":"QID520"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_43dIH6kWw5pRcto","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID521","SecondaryAttribute":"${q:\/\/QID446\/QuestionText} In more than 60 cases, judges looked at the election fraud allegations...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Disagree"},"3":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"4":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"5":{"Display":"Agree"},"6":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"CtlTrueCT2_Share","2":"CtlTrueCT2_Like","3":"CtlTrueCT2_Accuracy","4":"CtlTrueCT2_Manip","5":"CtlTrueCT2_ManipConf"},"ChoiceOrder":["4","5","3","1","2"],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would share this post on social media"},"2":{"Display":"I would 'like' this post on social media"},"3":{"Display":"This is an accurate post"},"4":{"Display":"This is a manipulative post"},"5":{"Display":"I am confident in my assessment of this post's manipulativeness"}},"Configuration":{"ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"MobileFirst":true,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","RepeatHeaders":"none","TextPosition":"inline","WhiteSpace":"OFF"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":7,"NextChoiceId":8,"QuestionDescription":"${q:\/\/Q